well...its been a really long time since i updated this thing...and ive been extremely bored all night long. im really pissed. someone hacked into my myspace account and deleted all my friends off my thing. now i only have about 1/3 of my friends i had before..that really pisses me off. oh well. the last couple weekends have been AMAZING! ive had sooo much fun! we had a hotel party after winter carnival last saturday night and...well...i was |NAKED|...i cant believe it still...lol...then this weekend i went to a frat party and got more drunk than ive ever been before...it was crazy/fun. anyways...things have changed since my last update i think..i prolly should have checked that before i wrote one on here..one thing is for sure..i am going to mankato minnesota for college next year with some of my closest friends..and leaving a lot of good friends behind here in this area...but i need to do what i need to do. im so confused as to what to do right now {sigh}. ill figure it out someday..or something.

so  its been a while since ive updated...and for good reason i guess...i thought things were going so well for me and gus...but it started out like last week..the whole me turning 18 in a couple days is really going to make it hard for us...so we broke up...then i thought we were back together...then he told me we werent..and that we just arent looking for the same thing in our lives right now...i dunno how to feel again..all i know is that i hope for that phone call someday soon telling me that he still wants to make it work..cuz he doesnt honestly understand how i feel...ive never wanted to be with someone sooo bad in my entire life..im the happiest person ever when im with him..hes really something special to me...i wish i could be as significant to him as he is to me. oh well...ive been broken like this enuff...im starting to get better with it, i hope...i dont wanna be like this anymore..i just want to be happy, with him. ughh...i hate this..

i am very upset today...i barely got any sleep and my eyes are extremely puffy...why cant things just ever work out for me. i thought things were going so GOOD! i guess not...i have never had such strong feelings for one single person. and for them to do what they have done to me..really sucks..and i absolutely hate this...i poured everything i had into this relationship...and ended up getting nothing...i hate this...it IS my life story..aghh...seriously what else can i do. what did i do wrong? i was nothing but a good guy to him...yeh yeh...nice guys finish last did come true i guess. its just not fair tho..and that really sucks. i want him SO bad...maybe in time..when he gets things figured out, right? yeh thats it...he just needs to realize some things...maybe being away from him for a little bit could be the best thing for us. maybe then he can realize what he had, and see what he has now...and then figure out that being with me was worth it? ughh..i hate this...........IM SICK OF CRYING TODAY!
